WEBVTT

00:10.600 --> 00:12.000
[Respect Copyright, Everyone's Responsibility]

01:06.540 --> 01:07.150
[The Eternal Fragrance]

01:07.150 --> 01:11.980
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

01:12.020 --> 01:15.140
[Episode 28]

01:20.030 --> 01:20.780
Come here.

01:24.440 --> 01:25.010
Your Highness!

01:31.270 --> 01:32.780
Your spirit energy comes from Lifei.

01:34.030 --> 01:35.250
Only by drawing on her spirit energy

01:36.270 --> 01:37.290
can you help me.

01:44.550 --> 01:45.060
Simo!

01:46.960 --> 01:47.650
Simo!

01:52.080 --> 01:52.620
Simo!

01:56.520 --> 01:57.290
Simo!

02:02.030 --> 02:02.810
Simo!

02:10.440 --> 02:11.170
Simo!

02:18.870 --> 02:19.740
Everything will be fine.

02:21.390 --> 02:22.180
Everything will be fine.

02:50.320 --> 02:51.940
The demons expected our arrival,

02:53.390 --> 02:54.370
so they left this.

02:58.550 --> 03:01.090
If we fail to hand over the Divine Tree by tomorrow's Chen hour,

03:02.800 --> 03:05.060
two more heads will be sent to us.

03:05.760 --> 03:06.530
Simo.

03:07.920 --> 03:09.020
Have you found Simo?

03:13.200 --> 03:13.780
Lifei,

03:14.390 --> 03:15.090
don't go over there.

03:56.590 --> 03:57.090
Lifei!

04:00.480 --> 04:00.970
Lifei!

04:15.870 --> 04:16.620
Simo,

04:18.760 --> 04:20.500
the mushrooms in the woods taste so fresh.

04:21.070 --> 04:23.790
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

04:23.790 --> 04:25.740
I even stole Elder Dongyang's chickens.

04:25.740 --> 04:27.570
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

04:28.030 --> 04:30.150
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

04:30.150 --> 04:31.250
Tender and full of flavor.

04:31.590 --> 04:33.790
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

04:34.830 --> 04:35.760
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

04:35.760 --> 04:36.660
Simo,

04:38.030 --> 04:38.770
in the next life...

04:39.030 --> 04:41.390
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

04:41.990 --> 04:43.510
♪No calamity can rival♪

04:43.710 --> 04:45.420
Can I be your sister in the next life?

04:45.420 --> 04:46.950
♪The lingering thread of a fragrance♪

04:49.090 --> 04:52.570
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

04:53.330 --> 04:55.570
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

04:56.010 --> 04:59.050
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge, past the pagoda♪

04:59.690 --> 05:01.970
♪In fine robes on galloping horses♪

05:02.770 --> 05:06.250
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

05:06.810 --> 05:09.090
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

05:09.610 --> 05:11.560
♪Betrayed by all, I still♪

05:11.560 --> 05:13.210
Lifei, what's wrong?

05:13.290 --> 05:15.490
♪Reign supreme♪

05:16.080 --> 05:19.120
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

05:20.960 --> 05:21.620
I'm fine.

05:24.910 --> 05:26.450
Since they're after me,

05:28.520 --> 05:30.250
I'll put an end to all this.

05:56.320 --> 05:56.890
Guardian,

05:57.230 --> 05:58.330
they wouldn't trade the Divine Tree

05:58.350 --> 05:59.770
for two ordinary disciples.

06:00.560 --> 06:01.660
Jiang Lifei

06:04.320 --> 06:05.570
will definitely come.

06:09.000 --> 06:09.690
Guardian,

06:10.080 --> 06:11.770
two disciples from the Wuyue Court are outside the valley.

06:11.960 --> 06:13.980
The female disciple claims she is the Divine Tree.

06:20.880 --> 06:21.940
Jiang Lifei,

06:22.880 --> 06:24.210
you've finally come.

06:25.230 --> 06:26.100
Where's Lei Xiuyuan?

06:26.680 --> 06:28.180
He's waiting for you, of course.

06:30.200 --> 06:31.010
After you.

06:31.760 --> 06:33.060
Release Changyue and Ye Ye,

06:33.560 --> 06:34.370
and I'll go with you.

06:51.390 --> 06:51.940
Ye.

06:53.790 --> 06:54.370
Are you alright?

07:31.080 --> 07:31.770
It turns out

07:32.790 --> 07:34.100
everything was destined long ago.

07:40.120 --> 07:40.740
How do you fare?

07:40.910 --> 07:41.660
Can you hold on?

07:42.390 --> 07:43.250
We're fine,

07:43.790 --> 07:45.500
but they took Simo away.

07:45.640 --> 07:46.370
Save him!

07:47.440 --> 07:48.100
No need.

07:49.960 --> 07:50.810
Simo

07:52.270 --> 07:53.420
has returned to the Wuyue Court.

07:54.440 --> 07:55.180
What about

07:55.560 --> 07:56.500
Lifei then?

07:56.960 --> 07:57.500
Don't worry,

07:57.680 --> 07:58.450
we've got a plan.

07:59.080 --> 07:59.770
That's a relief.

08:01.230 --> 08:02.450
We've scouted the valley.

08:03.150 --> 08:04.500
A hundred demons remain inside.

08:05.560 --> 08:06.810
Over fifty are in the southeast,

08:07.270 --> 08:08.540
more than thirty are in the west,

08:09.390 --> 08:10.180
and the fewest are in the east.

08:10.910 --> 08:11.500
Qiongqi

08:12.440 --> 08:13.620
is in the southeast.

08:15.520 --> 08:16.060
Where's Rakshasa?

08:16.560 --> 08:18.100
She's in the cave with Xiuyuan.

08:18.560 --> 08:19.740
I can't sense

08:21.080 --> 08:22.010
his heartbeat anymore.

08:25.270 --> 08:26.420
Take Ye Ye back to heal first.

08:26.560 --> 08:27.370
We'll stand guard here

08:27.390 --> 08:28.130
and wait for news from Lifei.

08:28.760 --> 08:29.300
Alright.

08:49.680 --> 08:50.970
He surely has a long life.

08:53.280 --> 08:55.020
Even pierced by thousands of vines, he still lives.

08:55.630 --> 08:57.260
You put him in this state.

08:57.510 --> 08:58.330
Hurry and save him!

09:01.080 --> 09:02.260
You killed Zhaomin,

09:02.960 --> 09:03.610
Elder Guangwei,

09:03.870 --> 09:04.970
and Simo,

09:05.510 --> 09:06.690
yet you still expect me to save him.

09:07.280 --> 09:08.610
Isn't that ridiculous?

09:11.400 --> 09:12.260
Do you believe

09:12.800 --> 09:14.690
I could kill you right now?

09:17.040 --> 09:18.420
Your Demon Lord is on his last legs.

09:19.280 --> 09:21.140
Killing or torturing me won't change a thing.

09:22.200 --> 09:23.020
You brought me here

09:23.750 --> 09:24.540
precisely to channel

09:24.560 --> 09:25.970
my spirit to sustain his life, right?

09:26.800 --> 09:28.090
Otherwise, he'll perish instantly.

09:32.630 --> 09:33.330
Jiang Lifei,

09:33.960 --> 09:36.180
you know well he never meant to harm you.

09:36.510 --> 09:37.090
He'd sacrifice

09:37.230 --> 09:38.690
his own life for you.

09:39.440 --> 09:40.060
What about you?

09:41.510 --> 09:42.660
Have you no heart at all?

09:53.630 --> 09:54.490
He has blood on his hands.

09:57.230 --> 09:59.060
What about all the lives he took?

10:00.750 --> 10:02.020
A murderer is a murderer,

10:02.710 --> 10:03.540
no excuses.

10:03.960 --> 10:04.690
Jiang Lifei,

10:05.630 --> 10:07.660
even if he wronged the whole world,

10:07.680 --> 10:09.300
he never wronged you.

10:10.280 --> 10:11.900
Because of you,

10:12.160 --> 10:13.380
he has ended up like this.

10:13.470 --> 10:14.450
You doubted him,

10:15.160 --> 10:16.940
and you killed him yourself.

10:22.280 --> 10:23.260
I never doubted him.

10:25.200 --> 10:27.690
But I can't let more people die for this.

10:36.870 --> 10:37.660
What are you doing?

10:40.510 --> 10:41.330
Let go.

10:41.830 --> 10:42.610
I'll save him.

10:55.280 --> 10:55.780
How...

10:56.200 --> 10:57.020
How will you save him?

11:16.080 --> 11:16.940
With my own blood.

11:54.160 --> 11:54.730
Xiuyuan,

11:55.710 --> 11:56.570
this must end.

12:10.200 --> 12:12.180
Activate the Four Symbols Divine Fire Formation with the Zhurong Stone

12:12.630 --> 12:13.780
and channel the Divine Tree's power

12:14.040 --> 12:15.060
to trap the demons

12:15.280 --> 12:16.690
and strip them of all strength.

12:17.440 --> 12:18.420
We'll charge in

12:18.920 --> 12:19.810
and wipe them all out at once.

12:30.440 --> 12:31.140
Lifei,

12:33.830 --> 12:34.730
why are you here?

12:42.440 --> 12:43.420
What's going on?

12:58.990 --> 13:00.490
Did Ji Tongzhou tell you to do this?

13:02.710 --> 13:03.420
Why?

13:05.160 --> 13:06.020
For Zhaomin

13:07.350 --> 13:08.660
and Simo.

13:10.920 --> 13:12.380
This is our destined fate.

13:29.040 --> 13:29.780
We've been trapped!

13:29.960 --> 13:31.540
The Divine Tree came to slay us.

14:19.280 --> 14:20.020
Stop!

14:25.200 --> 14:26.180
Stop!

14:43.680 --> 14:44.300
Lifei,

14:44.990 --> 14:46.140
you may take my life.

14:46.830 --> 14:48.180
Spare us from mutual slaughter.

14:50.960 --> 14:52.180
Grant me just a little more time,

14:53.280 --> 14:54.060
please.

14:54.230 --> 14:57.920
♪The warmth within my arms♪

14:58.440 --> 14:59.380
Grant you time?

14:59.380 --> 15:01.320
♪I can no longer hold on to♪

15:01.320 --> 15:03.020
So you can kill more people?

15:03.020 --> 15:04.590
♪In the cold night, how can I♪

15:04.590 --> 15:05.060
No.

15:06.040 --> 15:07.450
I will send them back to their homeland.

15:08.510 --> 15:09.420
Trust me.

15:09.420 --> 15:12.240
♪My heartbeat freezes♪

15:12.560 --> 15:15.760
♪I can no longer tell you♪

15:16.160 --> 15:19.360
♪Looking you in the eyes, I cannot♪

15:19.640 --> 15:22.680
♪Utter that line♪

15:23.040 --> 15:24.760
♪Knowing love and hate♪

15:25.080 --> 15:29.000
♪Pain and wounds cannot be stopped♪

15:30.360 --> 15:31.960
♪I still linger on♪

15:32.360 --> 15:36.560
♪Unwilling to let go of every inch of our past♪

15:36.960 --> 15:41.320
♪Last night's stars cast faint glimmers♪

15:41.600 --> 15:44.560
♪But we thought nothing of it♪

15:45.040 --> 15:45.610
Rakshasa.

15:45.610 --> 15:48.320
♪With a heartbroken cry♪

15:49.200 --> 15:49.780
Rakshasa.

15:49.780 --> 15:51.800
♪I wish you well♪

15:52.120 --> 15:53.800
♪Knowing right and wrong♪

15:54.160 --> 15:58.080
♪Black and gray are all illusions♪

15:59.440 --> 16:00.160
♪You're still screaming♪

16:00.160 --> 16:00.900
Rakshasa!

16:01.360 --> 16:05.110
♪Running relentlessly without regret♪

16:05.110 --> 16:05.730
Lifei,

16:07.110 --> 16:08.140
be careful not to hurt yourself.

16:08.140 --> 16:10.360
♪The storm looms, yet the wind stands in its way♪

16:10.720 --> 16:12.200
♪A final farewell left on the cliff♪

16:12.200 --> 16:13.850
Why won't any of you believe me?

16:13.850 --> 16:16.920
♪Leaping straight into that heartbreaking past♪

16:16.920 --> 16:18.260
Why?

16:20.570 --> 16:24.760
♪Just to keep you safe♪

16:40.800 --> 16:41.450
My Lord.

16:49.630 --> 16:51.210
Darn that Divine Tree.

16:52.470 --> 16:53.020
Watch out!

16:55.080 --> 16:55.660
Tongzhou!

16:56.440 --> 16:57.420
Everyone, follow me.

17:20.550 --> 17:21.290
Don't worry.

17:21.990 --> 17:23.860
Ye Ye's mostly healed from his wounds.

17:24.510 --> 17:25.820
Tongzhou will recover, too.

17:27.230 --> 17:28.900
All demons in Lilie Valley fled

17:29.510 --> 17:30.580
with the Demon Lord.

17:31.120 --> 17:32.450
They won't come after you again.

17:33.510 --> 17:34.380
It's all my fault.

17:36.710 --> 17:38.050
I truly am an ill omen.

17:39.880 --> 17:40.490
Lifei,

17:41.160 --> 17:42.100
don't blame yourself.

17:43.200 --> 17:43.900
I'm fine.

17:44.360 --> 17:45.050
Stay still.

17:45.550 --> 17:46.290
I'll heal you.

17:57.750 --> 17:58.490
Be careful.

18:02.030 --> 18:02.860
You're severely hurt.

18:03.600 --> 18:04.690
You should rest for a few more days.

18:08.960 --> 18:09.940
If I rest any longer,

18:10.880 --> 18:11.970
I'll become useless.

18:26.920 --> 18:27.340
Here.

18:35.680 --> 18:36.340
Lifei,

18:38.710 --> 18:39.970
do you still hate Xiuyuan?

18:50.470 --> 18:51.580
Between us,

18:53.790 --> 18:55.340
there is not even hatred left.

18:55.960 --> 18:56.530
Lifei,

18:57.680 --> 18:59.250
Xiuyuan didn't kill Simo.

19:00.230 --> 19:01.490
You met when you were young,

19:01.960 --> 19:03.530
endured countless hardships side by side,

19:04.120 --> 19:05.100
and loved each other deeply.

19:05.600 --> 19:07.010
Why not give him another chance?

19:21.640 --> 19:22.180
Look,

19:24.030 --> 19:25.290
the Fragrance Bond has vanished.

19:29.990 --> 19:31.100
From now on,

19:32.120 --> 19:33.530
there is no bond between us.

19:34.470 --> 19:35.340
I stand apart

19:36.710 --> 19:37.450
from him.

19:56.200 --> 19:57.050
There is no chance

19:59.310 --> 20:00.250
left for us.

20:02.990 --> 20:03.970
But the Divine Lord...

20:04.360 --> 20:05.050
Be careful.

20:06.750 --> 20:07.420
Xiuyuan's

20:09.550 --> 20:11.140
whole life has been fraught with misfortune.

20:11.880 --> 20:13.420
His greatest wish in this lifetime

20:14.440 --> 20:16.180
was to become an ordinary person

20:16.400 --> 20:17.690
and spend his days with you.

20:19.960 --> 20:20.970
May heaven show mercy to him,

20:21.960 --> 20:23.140
leaving him a way forward.

20:24.270 --> 20:27.180
Gelin and Lu Li sent word days ago

20:28.030 --> 20:30.420
that signs of the Sea Calamity have appeared in the East Sea.

20:33.510 --> 20:35.490
We'll eventually face a life-or-death battle.

20:36.790 --> 20:37.900
No one knows

20:38.680 --> 20:40.210
how many will survive after that.

21:21.400 --> 21:22.010
Master,

21:22.600 --> 21:23.290
at the hour of Mao today,

21:23.710 --> 21:24.900
the sea level of the East Sea dropped by eight inches.

21:25.270 --> 21:26.420
Five thousand li eastward across the waters,

21:26.550 --> 21:27.290
thunderclouds roiled endlessly.

21:27.750 --> 21:28.620
I can't tell what causes it.

21:31.640 --> 21:34.010
The heavenly thunder disaster is coming.

21:35.270 --> 21:37.620
The five-hundred-year Sea Calamity

21:39.030 --> 21:39.970
is upon us.

22:02.640 --> 22:03.210
My Lord.

22:03.310 --> 22:04.290
The Guardian has settled down.

22:04.470 --> 22:05.420
She is out of danger for now.

22:05.920 --> 22:06.340
I see.

22:09.960 --> 22:10.490
My Lord,

22:10.920 --> 22:12.210
our clansmen have rushed here.

22:16.880 --> 22:17.900
Five centuries have passed.

22:22.880 --> 22:23.940
It's time they came.

22:45.310 --> 22:45.820
Tongzhou!

22:47.070 --> 22:47.820
What happened?

22:58.640 --> 22:59.290
Lifei,

23:00.120 --> 23:00.820
I'm fine.

23:02.270 --> 23:03.530
Don't waste your spirit energy on me.

23:04.030 --> 23:05.730
Silence. Calm your breath to recover.

23:15.440 --> 23:16.100
Your Highness!

23:19.310 --> 23:19.940
Your Highness!

23:23.840 --> 23:24.970
What exactly is wrong with him?

23:25.470 --> 23:26.450
He hasn't fully healed,

23:26.840 --> 23:28.100
yet he forced himself to cultivate the Sacred Fire.

23:28.880 --> 23:30.380
I'll ease his spirit aura later.

23:30.710 --> 23:31.340
He should be alright.

23:31.750 --> 23:33.490
How could he possibly be alright?

23:35.230 --> 23:36.010
Lifei,

23:36.640 --> 23:38.450
he pushed himself to cultivate it for you.

23:39.440 --> 23:40.100
For me?

23:43.070 --> 23:46.210
His Highness was secluded in Duantu to break through,

23:47.070 --> 23:48.690
yet he rushed to the Wuyue Court

23:49.200 --> 23:50.250
to rescue you,

23:50.640 --> 23:52.100
leaving internal injuries back then.

23:52.360 --> 23:53.660
Then he fought battle after battle

23:53.790 --> 23:54.970
with no time to catch his breath.

23:55.920 --> 23:56.730
These days,

23:57.070 --> 23:58.380
crowds keep coming to confront him

23:58.400 --> 23:59.820
over the Divine Tree matter.

24:00.510 --> 24:02.250
He had to coax and deter them

24:02.270 --> 24:03.340
to send them away.

24:03.640 --> 24:05.100
He's worn himself ragged

24:05.920 --> 24:07.490
and now gravely wounded once more.

24:07.790 --> 24:09.010
He tried to accelerate his cultivation

24:09.310 --> 24:10.860
to recover early,

24:11.470 --> 24:11.940
so

24:12.790 --> 24:14.010
he could protect you.

24:15.400 --> 24:16.210
You're...

24:18.160 --> 24:19.100
You're Miaoqing?

24:21.440 --> 24:22.530
Why are you dressed like this?

24:25.790 --> 24:27.490
His Highness reshaped my body

24:28.840 --> 24:30.420
and mended my soul.

24:31.550 --> 24:32.290
I wish

24:33.470 --> 24:35.660
to stay by his side as a disciple

24:35.680 --> 24:36.860
of the Xingzheng Hall.

24:38.440 --> 24:39.970
My face bears scars,

24:41.440 --> 24:42.620
so I wear a veil.

24:45.310 --> 24:46.010
I'm sorry.

24:47.160 --> 24:48.580
You endured such terrible wounds for me,

24:49.120 --> 24:50.290
yet I failed to recognize you.

24:50.640 --> 24:51.450
Lifei,

24:52.470 --> 24:53.620
your sect suffered a catastrophe,

24:53.840 --> 24:55.010
and you had enough troubles.

24:55.710 --> 24:57.180
Naturally, you didn't recognize me.

24:58.230 --> 24:59.620
But I hope

25:01.160 --> 25:04.380
you understand how much His Highness endures.

25:05.510 --> 25:06.820
He has no one left

25:07.400 --> 25:08.580
but you now.

25:11.440 --> 25:12.730
Please stand by him.

25:15.920 --> 25:16.490
Don't worry.

25:18.790 --> 25:19.940
Tongzhou will pull through.

25:21.510 --> 25:22.690
I'll find a way to save him.

25:58.070 --> 25:58.730
What's wrong?

25:59.230 --> 26:00.380
Healed Tongzhou again?

26:01.470 --> 26:03.490
Even if the Divine Tree's spirit energy is boundless,

26:03.640 --> 26:05.100
don't exhaust it this way.

26:05.270 --> 26:06.580
Your body won't bear it.

26:07.120 --> 26:07.900
I'm fine.

26:08.960 --> 26:10.100
I'm tough,

26:10.270 --> 26:11.420
and just a short rest will do.

26:11.470 --> 26:12.010
You...

26:14.990 --> 26:16.010
Are your injuries healed?

26:18.640 --> 26:19.250
Look,

26:19.920 --> 26:20.620
much better now.

26:21.840 --> 26:22.420
Lifei,

26:23.230 --> 26:24.380
Changyue and I

26:25.030 --> 26:26.100
came to bid you farewell.

26:28.920 --> 26:30.100
Are you heading back to the Dizang Sect?

26:31.120 --> 26:32.380
There's no need to return

26:33.400 --> 26:34.010
to that shameful sect.

26:35.070 --> 26:35.730
The East Sea is in peril.

26:36.200 --> 26:37.290
Gelin has rushed back to the Wanxian Sect.

26:37.710 --> 26:39.820
We plan to head for the East Sea, too.

26:40.600 --> 26:41.730
Before that,

26:42.440 --> 26:43.620
we'll visit a place.

26:44.470 --> 26:45.580
Before Simo died,

26:46.030 --> 26:46.900
he asked us

26:48.510 --> 26:50.100
to visit his parents and family

26:50.510 --> 26:51.340
on his behalf.

26:54.360 --> 26:56.100
We're going to his hometown.

27:03.030 --> 27:04.380
When you see his parents,

27:04.600 --> 27:05.490
please give this to them for me.

27:11.270 --> 27:11.770
Alright.

27:12.920 --> 27:14.140
We'll meet in Duanming City.

27:33.160 --> 27:34.490
Patrol thoroughly.

27:35.270 --> 27:35.860
Yes.

28:05.310 --> 28:09.770
My Lord, thank you for using your energy to heal me.

28:10.600 --> 28:12.620
I deserve death for my mistakes.

28:13.470 --> 28:14.690
I even turned against you before.

28:14.710 --> 28:16.180
Let bygones be bygones.

28:19.200 --> 28:20.770
We're outside the mountain-sea barrier now.

28:21.840 --> 28:23.210
They won't chase us for the time being.

28:27.510 --> 28:28.940
The strange ocean currents lately

28:29.510 --> 28:31.180
are clear signs of the Sea Calamity.

28:32.230 --> 28:34.180
Our clansmen know you've returned

28:34.470 --> 28:35.940
and are hurrying here.

28:36.200 --> 28:38.380
What's your plan, My Lord?

28:48.550 --> 28:49.770
Once the Sea Calamity strikes,

28:50.440 --> 28:53.050
heavenly thunder and earth fire will shatter the mountain-sea barrier

28:53.400 --> 28:54.820
and engulf Duanming City.

28:55.440 --> 28:56.690
We can take this chance

28:56.880 --> 28:58.660
to avenge the siege of the Lilie Valley

28:59.360 --> 29:02.340
and avenge five centuries of shame upon our clan.

29:06.440 --> 29:07.420
The Sea Calamity shall consume the world

29:07.960 --> 29:08.940
and raze all the Central Plains.

29:09.640 --> 29:11.250
Do you think the demon clan will survive?

29:11.550 --> 29:13.210
At worst, we'll perish together.

29:14.030 --> 29:15.100
We crossed the sea,

29:15.600 --> 29:16.580
seeking a homeland,

29:17.440 --> 29:18.900
not a burial ground in a foreign land.

29:21.200 --> 29:22.860
Then what is your plan, My Lord?

29:25.310 --> 29:26.380
Stop this at once!

29:28.790 --> 29:29.530
Speak calmly.

29:41.550 --> 29:42.210
My Lord.

29:48.200 --> 29:49.940
Your return has lifted all our spirits.

29:50.270 --> 29:51.210
We should strike now,

29:51.550 --> 29:52.660
shatter the mountain-sea barrier,

29:52.990 --> 29:54.210
and catch them completely off guard.

29:56.440 --> 29:57.420
The battle at the Lilie Valley

29:57.990 --> 29:59.250
left our clan gravely weakened.

30:00.360 --> 30:02.050
Do you believe we can emerge unharmed

30:02.960 --> 30:04.180
if we wage another war now?

30:09.160 --> 30:10.140
The heavenly tribulation descends.

30:11.640 --> 30:13.690
If I witness you fighting each other again,

30:14.270 --> 30:16.940
I shall show no mercy.

30:18.750 --> 30:19.660
Understood.

30:45.400 --> 30:46.180
My Lord.

30:47.990 --> 30:48.620
My Lord,

30:49.030 --> 30:50.620
you look far more haggard

30:51.550 --> 30:53.140
than you did five centuries ago.

30:57.230 --> 30:58.290
Have you met me before?

30:59.070 --> 31:01.580
I had the honor of seeing you once

31:01.920 --> 31:03.730
back in our homeland overseas.

31:04.400 --> 31:05.770
In that lifetime,

31:05.990 --> 31:06.660
you promised

31:06.990 --> 31:08.490
you would lead our clansmen

31:08.920 --> 31:10.940
to find a blessed land to dwell in.

31:14.960 --> 31:15.660
A blessed land?

31:18.030 --> 31:19.900
Obviously, I've led you into an abyss.

31:20.510 --> 31:22.180
This is not your fault.

31:22.640 --> 31:24.970
Our clan is nurtured by the world's spirit nourishment.

31:25.200 --> 31:26.450
When the spiritual energy runs thin,

31:26.600 --> 31:28.100
sickness plagues us.

31:28.710 --> 31:31.210
The lands overseas have run dry of spirit energy.

31:31.510 --> 31:33.820
Countless clansmen have strange illnesses

31:33.960 --> 31:36.250
and can't survive.

31:36.400 --> 31:37.450
That is why

31:37.470 --> 31:40.140
we chose to follow you willingly.

31:40.270 --> 31:41.180
Yet we never imagined

31:42.160 --> 31:43.180
the Central Plains would not

31:44.120 --> 31:45.900
be a blessed land, either.

31:47.230 --> 31:48.450
I often think

31:48.790 --> 31:50.690
of our homeland.

31:51.270 --> 31:54.450
If I could return there before I die,

31:55.070 --> 31:57.140
I would die without regret.

31:58.120 --> 32:00.250
Perhaps our clan's decline

32:01.400 --> 32:03.380
is our destined fate.

32:04.510 --> 32:05.380
Destined fate?

32:08.920 --> 32:10.140
My Lord.

32:10.360 --> 32:11.530
Even if the destined fate

32:12.270 --> 32:13.450
can be turned around.

32:22.440 --> 32:23.050
Listen to me,

32:23.470 --> 32:24.730
don't push yourself hard in cultivation.

32:27.550 --> 32:28.140
And

32:28.710 --> 32:29.860
I don't need your protection.

32:30.360 --> 32:32.010
If anyone troubles you,

32:32.030 --> 32:32.860
send them straight to me.

32:34.750 --> 32:35.140
But...

32:35.230 --> 32:36.050
Have a good rest.

32:37.790 --> 32:38.290
Lifei.

32:38.640 --> 32:39.210
Lifei.

32:46.710 --> 32:47.210
Bring this

32:47.640 --> 32:48.380
with you.

32:50.550 --> 32:51.770
Those coveting the Divine Tree

32:52.360 --> 32:53.420
will never give up.

32:53.840 --> 32:55.010
Wear it, and it'll make them

32:55.440 --> 32:56.940
think twice before striking.

32:58.120 --> 32:58.970
From this day forward,

32:59.550 --> 33:00.290
you are the most important person

33:00.790 --> 33:02.820
to me, the Yue State and the Xingzheng Hall.

33:06.600 --> 33:07.250
Lifei,

33:07.960 --> 33:08.730
promise me.

33:09.270 --> 33:10.530
I will devote all I have

33:12.840 --> 33:13.940
to protect you forever.

33:18.360 --> 33:19.580
I know you mean well.

33:21.230 --> 33:21.860
Tongzhou,

33:22.510 --> 33:24.050
you will always be my closest friend.

33:25.600 --> 33:26.820
I have my own path to walk.

33:27.510 --> 33:29.210
I can't live under your protection forever.

33:30.070 --> 33:31.450
Are you still thinking of Lei Xiuyuan?

33:33.400 --> 33:34.580
He's the Demon Lord.

33:34.600 --> 33:35.660
It has nothing to do with him.

33:40.550 --> 33:41.690
Drink your medicine and rest early.

33:58.680 --> 33:59.340
Your Highness.

34:14.550 --> 34:15.490
Calm your anger.

34:16.550 --> 34:19.450
Lifei has just endured great difficulties

34:19.840 --> 34:21.170
with no mind for romantic affections.

34:21.880 --> 34:22.700
In time,

34:23.070 --> 34:25.300
she will understand your sincere heart.

34:27.800 --> 34:28.860
She understands everything,

34:30.880 --> 34:32.700
but she refuses to accept me.

34:35.920 --> 34:36.700
Then

34:39.070 --> 34:40.090
will you let go?

34:45.280 --> 34:46.010
No.

34:49.720 --> 34:50.780
If that's the case,

34:52.190 --> 34:54.300
your genuine devotion

34:54.960 --> 34:56.860
will eventually win her heart.

35:29.960 --> 35:32.300
Her Divine Tree spirit energy works wonders indeed.

35:58.320 --> 35:59.010
Miaoqing,

36:03.590 --> 36:05.010
would you be my Lifei?

36:07.840 --> 36:08.940
I shall obey

36:09.720 --> 36:11.260
whatever you command.

36:20.510 --> 36:21.300
It's a pity

36:23.670 --> 36:24.820
that you're not her.

36:53.150 --> 36:54.050
The Sea Calamity draws near.

36:55.400 --> 36:57.130
Lifei will head to Duanming City.

36:58.400 --> 37:00.220
I must stop hiding in the academy.

37:02.150 --> 37:04.650
Master, please let me go.

37:16.670 --> 37:17.380
Very well.

37:17.960 --> 37:20.010
When the nest falls, no egg stays intact.

37:20.510 --> 37:21.490
We cultivate immortality

37:21.990 --> 37:23.380
precisely for such moments.

37:23.960 --> 37:26.300
If we can avert this calamity,

37:26.960 --> 37:28.700
it shall be a blessing for all living beings.

37:31.720 --> 37:33.130
Cuixuan damaged your spirit meridians.

37:33.550 --> 37:34.260
If you go,

37:34.840 --> 37:37.260
never recklessly wield your spirit energy.

37:37.590 --> 37:40.010
Otherwise, it'll cost you your life.

37:40.630 --> 37:41.420
I shall remember.

37:43.550 --> 37:44.170
Please

37:45.320 --> 37:47.050
look after Mu.

37:48.070 --> 37:49.420
Rest assured.

37:50.670 --> 37:52.700
She is part of our academy.

37:53.400 --> 37:55.130
The academy will keep her safe.

38:34.440 --> 38:34.970
Mu,

38:37.590 --> 38:38.740
I'm leaving soon.

38:40.990 --> 38:41.940
But

38:43.470 --> 38:45.490
I have no idea when I'll be back.

38:46.510 --> 38:47.740
There's something I've hidden

38:49.800 --> 38:50.970
from you all this time.

38:52.550 --> 38:53.260
Mu,

38:55.470 --> 38:56.700
actually, I'm Yecha,

38:58.720 --> 39:00.090
another Guardian of the demon clan.

39:05.400 --> 39:08.010
During the war against the immortals five centuries ago,

39:09.470 --> 39:10.530
I was cast into the bottom of the sea.

39:12.190 --> 39:13.130
When I woke,

39:14.550 --> 39:15.940
I'd transformed into a boy

39:15.960 --> 39:17.530
of eleven or twelve.

39:34.510 --> 39:35.380
I refused to give up

39:37.110 --> 39:38.340
and wanted to take revenge on Qingcheng.

39:39.190 --> 39:40.650
I tracked him down by every means

39:42.240 --> 39:43.570
and followed him in secret.

39:45.240 --> 39:45.740
Yet I found him

39:45.760 --> 39:47.940
gathering the bones of my fallen clansmen

39:49.110 --> 39:50.380
and building the Outcast Tomb.

40:06.030 --> 40:07.570
I thought it was hypocrisy

40:08.470 --> 40:09.570
and resolved to slay him.

40:11.150 --> 40:12.260
So I snuck up to strike him

40:12.760 --> 40:13.860
from behind,

40:18.190 --> 40:19.130
but he sensed my attack.

40:23.720 --> 40:27.300
All my memories were gone when I regained consciousness.

40:29.440 --> 40:30.940
As I had no one to rely on,

40:32.240 --> 40:33.170
Qingcheng set aside our enmity

40:34.190 --> 40:35.090
and took me as his disciple.

40:53.880 --> 40:57.380
As time passed, my memories slowly returned.

40:58.630 --> 41:01.740
But I grew as close to him as father and son

41:03.030 --> 41:04.820
and could not bring myself to harm him.

41:06.240 --> 41:06.940
Later,

41:07.990 --> 41:09.820
as I had grown up,

41:10.440 --> 41:12.010
he sent me to the Chufeng Academy

41:13.510 --> 41:14.740
to let me learn

41:15.190 --> 41:16.650
what a true immortal sect is like.

41:17.840 --> 41:18.530
After that,

41:19.440 --> 41:20.420
I went to the Wuyue Court

41:21.320 --> 41:22.820
and became a disciple of Master Guangwei.

41:23.630 --> 41:24.490
That was when I met you.

41:26.760 --> 41:27.780
Master Qingcheng

41:28.920 --> 41:30.420
always knew my nature.

41:31.670 --> 41:32.650
He firmly believed

41:33.280 --> 41:35.170
immortals and demons would reconcile.

41:37.070 --> 41:40.130
He spent his whole life striving for that,

41:40.550 --> 41:42.740
gathering countless ancient scrolls and treasures.

41:43.240 --> 41:44.260
I'll bring all of them

41:44.800 --> 41:46.090
with me to the East Sea.

41:47.670 --> 41:50.090
I hope I can fulfill his lifelong aspiration

41:50.960 --> 41:53.570
and find a chance for reconciliation.

41:56.440 --> 41:57.900
Let's check over there.

41:58.150 --> 41:58.860
Yes.

42:10.990 --> 42:14.010
With the Xuantian power, open the Biluo Path.

42:14.510 --> 42:17.610
Follow this compass, and you may return to the land overseas.

42:22.920 --> 42:24.220
To lead my clansmen back home,

42:25.590 --> 42:28.970
I must find the Xuantian Biluo Plate.

42:37.440 --> 42:38.170
It's the curse.

42:39.670 --> 42:40.700
Have I not much time left?

42:42.050 --> 42:42.360
[The Eternal Fragrance]

42:42.360 --> 42:44.560
[Adapted from Shisilang's novel, The Eternal Fragrance]

42:55.800 --> 42:59.480
♪I trade all the mortal world's splendor♪

42:59.800 --> 43:02.480
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

43:02.560 --> 43:05.800
♪Our fates intertwined, embracing yet fighting♪

43:05.800 --> 43:09.080
♪The hardest bond to balance♪

43:09.200 --> 43:13.080
♪Obsessed and struggling, a thousand thoughts arise♪

43:13.360 --> 43:16.560
♪Love sprouts again in this lifetime♪

43:16.720 --> 43:22.800
♪No calamity can rival the lingering thread of a fragrance♪

43:23.080 --> 43:27.200
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

43:27.480 --> 43:30.160
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

43:30.360 --> 43:32.280
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

43:32.400 --> 43:36.720
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

43:36.880 --> 43:40.720
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

43:41.080 --> 43:44.080
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

43:44.160 --> 43:50.280
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

43:50.480 --> 43:54.200
♪With you, we melt into mist and haze♪

44:07.440 --> 44:11.200
♪I trade the highest heaven and endless clouds♪

44:11.400 --> 44:14.200
♪For a fleeting moment with you♪

44:14.280 --> 44:17.680
♪Pierced by countless arrows, pain and illness pile on♪

44:17.680 --> 44:21.000
♪Yet I remain silent♪

44:21.160 --> 44:25.000
♪Deep love and long yearning, a kiss falls into a dream♪

44:25.160 --> 44:28.360
♪In the distant night, bitterness blooms♪

44:28.600 --> 44:34.440
♪The grand chapter is rewritten, startling the whole world♪

44:35.000 --> 44:38.920
♪With you, through mountains falling and seas turning to sand♪

44:39.200 --> 44:41.960
♪Withered branches burst into bloom♪

44:42.160 --> 44:44.000
♪Hand in hand on the Naihe Bridge♪

44:44.160 --> 44:48.360
♪Past the pagoda, in fine robes on galloping horses♪

44:48.600 --> 44:52.480
♪Always, at the very end of obsession♪

44:52.720 --> 44:55.760
♪Comes that one moment of softness♪

44:55.960 --> 45:02.680
♪Betrayed by all, I still reign supreme♪

45:02.720 --> 45:06.680
♪If the seal can't be broken, then let it go♪

45:06.920 --> 45:09.680
♪Where the heart finds peace, there is home♪

45:09.800 --> 45:11.720
♪Side by side, we fly through seas of clouds♪

45:11.880 --> 45:16.160
♪Break through the waves; the heart's ocean knows no shore♪

45:16.360 --> 45:20.200
♪Always, at the very end of fate♪

45:20.440 --> 45:23.560
♪Comes that one moment of defiance♪

45:23.600 --> 45:29.600
♪In the human world or above, like flowing water and falling petals♪

45:30.000 --> 45:34.360
♪Let this fleeting life be whatever it may♪
